'We booked this hotel because of the wonderful reviews but were quite disappointed. The superior room was average with thin walls so you could hear all your neighbors and a tiny bathroom. The appointments were good but inconsistent. Sheets were stiff and the duvet was way too heavy. Sometimes there was drinking water in the evening, sometimes not. Sometimes the room was very clean, sometimes not. The communal areas in the lobby were not very special. The Sport shop in the hotel was horrible. Unattentive, unfriendly service. The equipment was poorly maintained. The prices were 50